Jimmy's autobiography, I Walked with the Giants:  https://amzn.to/2q5hLBr

Jimmy Heath and John Coltrane were young musicians caught in the magic of Bebop as played by Charlie Parker and Dizzy Gillespie in the late 40s.  This excerpt is from "Passing the Torch," a documentary about Jazz mentors.  To view on Amazon Prime:  https://www.amazon.com/Passing-Torch-Jimmy-Heath/dp/B071LFRQDF/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1499727832&sr=8-1&
title: Jimmy Heath:  Trane's Work Ethic
